descp2: string, type, list of types or None (default="numeric") Data type of result. If None, the dtype of the input is preserved. If "numeric", dtype is preserved unless array.dtype is object. If dtype is a list of types, conversion on the first type is only performed if the dtype of the input is not in the list.
